<section id=3D"1">
<h5>When to use?</h5>



<p>Deciding which statistical method to use to analyze your data can be a c=
hallenging task. Whether a statistical method is appropriate for your data =
is partly determined by the <a href=3D"https://statkat.com/statistical-tech=
nique-selection/measurement-levels.php" target=3D"_self"> measurement level=
</a> of your variables.=20

The cochran's q test requires the following variable types:=20


